{"tid":221542,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"［神秘學］招挑花方法分享區","createTime":"2017-04-28T18:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T05:28:03.000Z","uid":54046,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42f885fe71a9be076114486b0905fe95d6e6f1f5","tid":221542,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T18:37:35.000Z","msg":"呢個post希望可以集合到不同招桃花或者和合上既方法<br />\n<br />\n我自己首先講幾個先<br />\n希望整合後可以比神秘學jj作參考用<br />\n<br />\n1. 奇門遁甲擅用玉女守門格<br />\n用玉女守門格搵方式約女神<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.divinehere.com/column/16alanlo/0616016.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.divinehere.com%2Fcolumn%2F16alanlo%2F0616016.html&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=d1352b7f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.divinehere.com/column/16alanlo/0616016.html</a><br />\n<br />\n向玉女守門格局方向走1080步，其間再念玉女神咒<br />\n以增桃花<br />\n<br />\n2. 帶粉晶或粉晶七星陣 <br />\n<br />\n3. 佛牌<br />\n正路既會帶坤平，蝴蝶，人緣鳥等等<br />\n<br />\n4. 拜和合二仙/月老<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1537572/%E8%84%AB%E7%8D%A8%E6%B1%82%E6%83%85%E7%B7%A3%20%20%20%20%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%9C%80%E9%9D%88%E9%A9%97%E5%A7%BB%E7%B7%A3%E5%BB%9F%E6%8E%A8%E4%BB%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1537572%2F%25E8%2584%25AB%25E7%258D%25A8%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%25B7%25A3%2520%2520%2520%2520%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%259D%2588%25E9%25A9%2597%25E5%25A7%25BB%25E7%25B7%25A3%25E5%25BB%259F%25E6%258E%25A8%25E4%25BB%258B&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=0a3c657c\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1537572/%E8%84%AB%E7%8D%A8%E6%B1%82%E6%83%85%E7%B7%A3%20%20%20%20%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%9C%80%E9%9D%88%E9%A9%97%E5%A7%BB%E7%B7%A3%E5%BB%9F%E6%8E%A8%E4%BB%8B</a><br />\n<br />\n5.拜狐仙<br />\n香港有，但唔清楚佢地有無料<br />\n<br />\n6.修持懷愛法<br />\n有興趣再講"},{"pid":"c4c78421d75e15c378467436eff040c2139ec34e","tid":221542,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi