uote><br />\n人緣粉？</blockquote><br />\n係呀 work唔work 架</blockquote><br />\n睇邊個師傅做囉<br />\n佛牌我都有，不過唔係香港請既<br />\n我係去泰國搵司機車我地去搵師傅請<br />\n我信唔過香港班仆街<br />\n我有人緣油"},{"pid":"f1319b47f61dd7e14f9137cac3e59f5854521ca3","tid":221542,"uid":16657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T20:26:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地盤仲要坤官不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n值符落坤宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468bd9a04b4a1196a0d96a90b9197d9e1e817bed","tid":221542,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T21:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地盤仲要坤官不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 六合加坤宮"},{"pid":"1208cd1fc16f2143f071e605c2ce093c0f5ba280","tid":221542,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T04:50:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>地盤仲要坤官不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 六合加坤宮</blockquote><br />\n如果時間無得改既話，呢個方向算係咁"},{"pid":"8bbc8332e6f5298997f4232e31761d6407d5bfe0","tid":221542,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T04:57:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>地盤仲要坤官不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n值符落坤宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n覺得無問題咪用囉<br />\n睇你想要咩架姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d34c8b43792523eacb3ebbcf682f8f1b380ede","tid":221542,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T05:00:47.000Z","msg":"叫佢地修懷愛法<br />\n又唔係即修修有、搞黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好比依d 我執整衰密法個朵<br />\n已經比出邊d人講話點點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nrule of thumb 叫人唔好亂係唔岩根器既人面前提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88f9975dcb54bf711123b5c93bc90dc5329eb23","tid":221542,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T05:28:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫佢地修懷愛法<br />\n又唔係即修修有、搞黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好比依d 我執整衰密法個朵<br />\n已經比出邊d人講話點點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nrule of thumb 叫人唔好亂係唔岩根器既人面前提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時引左佢地入黎，之後就會開始聽道理<br />\n見最多既係奶左野搵仁波切搞<br />\n之後就開始修"}]}